1362
03:12:03,736 --> 03:12:04,056
Thank you.

1363
03:12:04,076 --> 03:12:18,924
Sometimes I ask questions that make me laugh because I'm the only man in this at this table, but I'm guessing all of you have stood in a line to use the bathroom as women while there's no line for the men's room.

1364
03:12:19,224 --> 03:12:21,825
And the women's line is not true.

1365
03:12:22,685 --> 03:12:26,687
I'm just saying like, I just was talking about this with Jenny the other day.

1366
03:12:26,707 --> 03:12:29,829
I don't even remember what we were talking about, but that

1367
03:12:30,202 --> 03:12:35,264
you know, the line, somehow society has still not figured out that women need a little more time in the bathroom.

1368
03:12:35,964 --> 03:12:52,371
And I guess I'm just, from my own students' perspective, you know, and from other students' perspectives, students used to not want to use the bathrooms because they didn't think they were clean enough or they weren't safe enough.

1369
03:12:52,955 --> 03:13:04,477
And now it's just not worth it sometimes for the amount of time it takes to use a bathroom is what I'm hearing.

1370
03:13:04,897 --> 03:13:12,978
And so students not drinking and eating isn't really conducive to the best being prepared for an education.

1371
03:13:13,058 --> 03:13:21,660
So if you're telling me that the girls can get in and out of the bathrooms just as fast as the boys,

1372
03:13:24,005 --> 03:13:29,167
You're all the professionals on what it means to be a female waiting in line for a bathroom.

1373
03:13:30,148 --> 03:13:31,108
I'm obviously not.

1374
03:13:31,288 --> 03:13:37,251
And as a man, I will say that I just don't know how you all put up with it.

1375
03:13:37,711 --> 03:13:43,114
Every single time I go to any place where there's crowds, I cannot believe you don't revolt.

1376
03:13:44,194 --> 03:13:44,795
And so-

1377
03:13:48,898 --> 03:14:02,636
I still can't believe that two people, and honestly, I don't know what the lawyers would have to say if we said the rule is different for the girls versus the boys, but I certainly can't believe that two girls at the time is enough.

1378
03:14:03,157 --> 03:14:06,358
to get all of our students through the bathrooms that are open?

1379
03:14:06,418 --> 03:14:22,023
So there were only three stalls, but not only that, I think now that there are the new rules in place and the students are hanging their placards, they're going in, they're doing their business and they're coming right back out.

1380
03:14:23,024 --> 03:14:25,845
I think before they were going in and

1381
03:14:28,317 --> 03:14:37,683
Yes, that level of socializing, if you don't have a group of people to socialize with, there are only two people, you're gonna just go in, do your business and come out.

1382
03:14:38,283 --> 03:14:44,267
So even the times that I've done bathroom duty, it's pretty quick.

1383
03:14:44,287 --> 03:14:49,430
They go in, they know they might see two or three people waiting, they go in, they come out, they go in, they come out.

1384
03:14:50,871 --> 03:14:54,113
And where you have the bathroom stacked,

1385
03:14:55,154 --> 03:15:02,381
If one area were to have a slightly longer line, they know they can just go up one floor, which some students have done.

1386
03:15:02,401 --> 03:15:02,861
Okay.

1387
03:15:03,081 --> 03:15:04,423
Or up a floor or down a floor.

1388
03:15:04,443 --> 03:15:06,344
I mean, I've seen it happen.

1389
03:15:06,485 --> 03:15:11,369
I'll just have to trust you on this, because I don't really spend much time in women's bathrooms, but thank you.

1390
03:15:11,449 --> 03:15:11,970
